</li>
<li><p id="_2653adde-5881-0243-578c-21545f07fe3c">IEC Electropedia: available at <link target="https://www.electropedia.org"/></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p id="_9bcb5fe1-17a6-d4fc-01b8-bd4cfa278b0e">For the purposes of this document, the following terms and definitions apply.</p>

