</admitted>



<definition id="_7b858d27-e90e-2c2d-3dbe-d8bca4980c8c"><verbal-definition id="_ab81ae37-1d69-d51b-28e8-6642a9c825a9"><p id="_51f30d46-d4ca-82af-eab8-001106788fda">kernel, whole or broken, which has changed its normal colour as a result of heating</p></verbal-definition></definition>


 <termnote id="_e74059e2-52ae-af77-2370-e5a30a596137"><p id="_fd8442d5-0d5d-33b9-3d41-a4bcb04e8b41">This category includes whole or broken kernels that are yellow due to alteration. Parboiled rice in a batch of non-parboiled rice is also included in this category.</p>
</termnote></term>

