  <script>Latn</script>
  <script>Cyrl</script>
  <abstract language="en" script="Latn">ISO 7301:2011 gives the minimum specifications for rice (Oryza sativa L.) which is subject to international trade. It is applicable to the following types: husked rice and milled rice, parboiled or not, intended for direct human consumption. It is neither applicable to other products derived from rice, nor to waxy rice (glutinous rice).</abstract>
